{"tid":1247824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日夏至】孖發哥德斌鮑姐行山 江美儀：跑到上山冇風","createTime":"2019-06-21T08:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T10:46:44.000Z","uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"89944b5483a86dbea514c3c7b2ee5a561b46a455","tid":1247824,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"影帝周潤發喜歡行山，不時相約圈中朋友行山兼親親大自然，今日（21日）夏至，發哥聯同江美儀﹑方中信﹑米雪﹑鮑起靜和黃德斌等，齊齊去大帽山行山，江美儀在社交網上載由發哥親自操刀的合照，個個都笑容滿面，並舉起勝利手勢，江美儀說：「今日夏至，果然係熱嘅！跑到上山都無風，如果喺户外工作嘅朋友，飲多啲水呀！#江美人 #江美儀 #好好善待自己 #我要運動我要健康 #我行山師傅係發哥。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZAM8MxZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZAM8MxZ.jpg&h=1825f364&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c60f4a0ee32427472f96ec82bf86681812726e7","tid":1247824,"uid":77277,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"發哥又話民間特首又盛<br />\n<br />\n反送中佢潛水"},{"pid":"e8ede8361c3a4ecea01f9b13d6579e2a89fa91f5","tid":1247824,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"吃喝玩樂！<br />\nRip"},{"pid":"e65726f6bf29eb1e248a95581712489d3e1f7cab","tid":1247824,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"棋靈王"},{"pid":"94270820a430f7be53737e3ad38151ecbe7a9fba","tid":1247824,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:54:13.000Z","msg":"咁能開心"},{"pid":"101f5c9fb28d85dfc007daa9a0cb6fe8538fc196","tid":1247824,"uid":65371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:55:00.000Z","msg":"兄弟行山"},{"pid":"7714d63eeec68cc4384157910dfd44160e5d8867","tid":1247824,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"民間特首係網民老屈佢,佢一向唔多出聲個堆來"},{"pid":"48ffe2aa080555ebd3df45966514e21717ceb165","tid":1247824,"uid":9053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"等睇連登仔看圖作文"},